 Plot1<- ggplot(data = D1, aes(x = lifeExp, y = gdpPercap, color = continent, size = pop)) +
 theme_bw() +
  scale_y_continuous(trans = "sqrt")+
  geom_point() +
  facet_wrap(~D1$year) +
  labs(size = "Population(100k)")
